{"tid":262293,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"好難識到香港女仔","createTime":"2017-05-29T06:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T06:52:00.000Z","uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83ab93d12e391526eba07f3e709066305ab3fd49","tid":262293,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:12:14.000Z","msg":"本人係男仔黎<br />\n今年36歲<br />\n咁多年都無拍過拖<br />\n有主動識人，也有被人追過<br />\n但點解識親都係過客無結果？<br />\n我街度見啲靚女成日拖住啲醜男<br />\n但整體我樣外型一啲都唔差<br />\n但都吸引唔到女仔黎認識<br />\n自問都幾專一，唔煙唔酒，又踏實，又成日做運動，又健談，點解無人識？<br />\n<br />\n心裡感覺真係好孤獨，經常都係一個人過<br />\n朋友又唔算多，但我又唔鐘意夜蒲<br />\n都算乖仔架喇，無不良嚐好<br />\n交網友有啲傾傾下會消失<br />\n什至好現實唔so自己什至刪埋你<br />\n香港女仔真係咁難識<br />\n<br />\n有冇女仔可以入黎傾下<br />\n本人係單身"},{"pid":"265d3cb0ce3eaaa4987366f0fb14b74be089f59b","tid":262293,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"搵幾錢個月，資產有幾多？"},{"pid":"a26847ddf9d8ef82e125b676bd969053e084f06b","tid":262293,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵幾錢個月，資產有幾多？</blockquote><br />\n做保安月入14000"},{"pid":"bac33714f649734e155f73496a4daed05096b128","tid":262293,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1658dfd4ae04781607808133727da484e422ed46","tid":262293,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"假膠唔好理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a6629d4a5d97d2f928cb316931e721b76b014a","tid":262293,"uid":96595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0beda78e5202e287bd4ab6a2d461df996ca3d1e1","tid":262293,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:24:17.000Z","msg":"有無請人飲油"},{"pid":"f79b622eb